            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer of the maftǝḥe śǝrāy-type using ʾasmāt like <foreign xml:lang="gez">አኽያ፡ ሹራህያ፡ አልሻዳይ፡</foreign>, which 
                    occur also in <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4704MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta māʿśǝromu la-ʾagānǝnt</ref>, <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6854Prayer">Prayer for binding the demons, containing ʾasmāt</ref>,
                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6830PPAyna">Protective prayer against evil eye (ʿāyna ṭǝlā wa-ʿāyna zār
          wa-šotalāy), with ʾasmāt</ref> and <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6812MagicPr">Magic prayer to bind the demons</ref>.</p>
